[This is a work of fiction]

2
00:02:12,250 --> 00:02:15,200
[Episode 7]
[A Humble Life Holds Endless Potential]

3
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:30,410
Ping'an was imprisoned

4
00:02:31,850 --> 00:02:32,780
and accused of being involved
in the military fund case.

5
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:34,780
Which scoundrel

6
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:35,620
leaked the information?

7
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:37,530
I suspect it was Yuan Shaocheng.

8
00:02:37,690 --> 00:02:38,410
Ping'an set him up before,

9
00:02:38,690 --> 00:02:39,620
causing him to be tortured by Du Liang.

10
00:02:39,970 --> 00:02:41,060
Looks like he's holding a grudge.

11
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:42,650
It's possible.

12
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:43,970
But...

13
00:02:45,690 --> 00:02:46,250
But what?

14
00:02:47,020 --> 00:02:47,810
If it was him,

15
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,250
why hasn't anyone

16
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:50,370
come to capture us yet?

17
00:02:51,370 --> 00:02:52,780
Who else could it be if not him?

18
00:02:53,130 --> 00:02:54,340
Ping'an has already told us

19
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,060
he's

20
00:02:55,250 --> 00:02:56,300
cunning and cruel.

21
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:57,020
It's no surprise

22
00:02:57,130 --> 00:02:57,690
he'd do something

23
00:02:57,810 --> 00:02:58,940
like burning bridges.

24
00:02:59,810 --> 00:03:00,850
The fact that he
hasn't come for you two yet

25
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:01,690
might mean

26
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:02,620
he's plotting something worse.

27
00:03:04,020 --> 00:03:05,250
Was she sent to the prison
of the Court of Judicial Review?

28
00:03:06,690 --> 00:03:07,340
No,

29
00:03:08,530 --> 00:03:09,530
she was taken away by Li Jun.

30
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:11,810
Oh, no.

31
00:03:12,180 --> 00:03:12,900
Falling into his hands

32
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:14,060
is worse than death.

33
00:03:15,090 --> 00:03:16,130
I'm going to rescue Ping'an now.

34
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:16,940
Cailian,

35
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,300
don't lose your composure.

36
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:21,300
Let's come up with a plan first.

37
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,940
♪The residual glow of twilight
brushes across my brows♪

38
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,980
♪While the sorrowful rain lingers,
unwilling to dissipate♪

39
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:38,980
♪Life is but a fleeting dream,
like smoke♪

40
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:42,180
♪Slipping away in the haze of time♪

41
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:47,000
♪Grief reflects in my eyes♪

42
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:50,940
♪And I am left to say the final goodbye♪

43
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:55,060
♪This tragic scene♪

44
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:57,860
♪Replays over and over♪

45
00:04:00,060 --> 00:04:03,180
♪Seasons change♪

46
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:07,260
♪Life withers and blooms in turn,
yet I remain burdened with regret♪

47
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:11,220
♪Like flames consuming the body♪

48
00:04:11,340 --> 00:04:14,500
♪The pain sears through promises♪

49
00:04:16,540 --> 00:04:18,660
♪Whose tears have melted♪

50
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:20,220
♪The cold fragments of the past♪

51
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:23,580
♪Piecing together this lonely world?♪

52
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:28,380
♪Hands intertwined,
symbolizing enduring affection♪

53
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:31,260
♪Love becomes eternal♪

54
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:36,180
♪As the sun sets♪

55
00:04:47,810 --> 00:04:48,890
The liquor I have here

56
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,010
is average.

57
00:04:51,250 --> 00:04:52,330
But when you're promoted,

58
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:54,130
I'll take you to Mei Mansion

59
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,250
to sample finer ones.

60
00:05:02,620 --> 00:05:03,130
Now,

61
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:04,770
I am under your command.

62
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:06,330
If you have anything to say, Mr. Hai,

63
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,420
please go ahead.

64
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:10,740
Let me ask you something.

65
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:12,860
What exactly is your relationship

66
00:05:13,570 --> 00:05:14,860
with Ye Ping'an?

67
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,940
I've only known her
for less than half a month.

68
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:18,770
Currently,

69
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:20,810
we are merely carrying out

70
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:22,100
an assigned task together.

71
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:23,450
That's good.

72
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:25,570
Right now, you're in the midst

73
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:26,940
of an important promotion.

74
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:28,420
You know who should be helped

75
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,500
and who shouldn't.

76
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:33,100
You're a smart person.

77
00:05:33,810 --> 00:05:34,740
That's all

78
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:35,810
I need to say.

79
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:47,420
After such a victory tonight,

80
00:05:48,770 --> 00:05:49,620
why do you look like this?

81
00:05:50,210 --> 00:05:50,890
It's nothing.

82
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:53,980
I just feel a little sad.

83
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,130
Sad?

84
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:00,540
So it's because of that Ye Ping'an,
isn't it?

85
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:03,770
When I first met her,

86
00:06:05,210 --> 00:06:06,570
I thought she was just a fraud.

87
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:08,500
What about afterward?

88
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:09,740
Afterward,

89
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,860
I realized that encountering her,
this venomous creature,

90
00:06:15,570 --> 00:06:17,010
was like a game of chess
with a worthy opponent.

91
00:06:17,450 --> 00:06:18,570
There aren't many who can be called

92
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:19,300
your opponent.

93
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:21,420
So, who exactly

94
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:23,330
wants her dead?

95
00:06:27,010 --> 00:06:28,010
I don't need you to tell me.
I already know.

96
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:29,330
It's Hai Yiping, isn't it?

97
00:06:30,450 --> 00:06:31,500
Don't look at me like that.

98
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:33,250
The only person who can make you

99
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,210
weigh your options right now

100
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:36,420
is Mr. Hai.

101
00:06:37,010 --> 00:06:38,420
Normally,
I just can't be bothered to think.

102
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:39,660
You don't actually think
I'm foolish, do you?

103
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:42,330
Hesheng,

104
00:06:42,770 --> 00:06:44,420
I don't usually say it,

105
00:06:45,010 --> 00:06:46,130
but I know exactly what you're doing.

106
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:48,810
Whenever

107
00:06:49,770 --> 00:06:51,180
there's a chance to stand out
in front of others,

108
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:53,450
you always step aside
and let me take the lead.

109
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:54,450
It's all for me

110
00:06:54,620 --> 00:06:55,660
to earn more credit,

111
00:06:56,690 --> 00:06:57,620
so that we,

112
00:06:59,010 --> 00:07:00,540
the people of Mang Gutter,

113
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:03,010
can break free
from the lower status faster.

114
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:12,250
I know you don't let emotions

115
00:07:12,330 --> 00:07:13,250
cloud your judgment,

116
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,330
but as for Ye Ping'an,

117
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:19,770
are you really not going to save her?

118
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:41,810
If you're still hesitating,

119
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:42,980
maybe it's best

120
00:07:43,540 --> 00:07:44,540
to leave the decision to fate.

121
00:08:03,010 --> 00:08:05,300
I fear not the chill wind
rising from within.

122
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:10,130
I wait only for the scent
of plum blossoms to fill the air.

123
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:13,810
Torture

124
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:16,130
is an art,

125
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:19,980
and your wounds

126
00:08:20,890 --> 00:08:22,100
are like crimson plum blossoms

127
00:08:22,370 --> 00:08:23,420
blooming in the darkness.

128
00:08:28,010 --> 00:08:28,690
Look.

129
00:08:29,210 --> 00:08:30,300
Don't they resemble white snow

130
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:32,140
drifting onto the branches?

131
00:08:32,490 --> 00:08:34,380
The sweat drawn by pain
still carries a subtle fragrance.

132
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:37,330
It perfectly matches this verse.

133
00:08:39,610 --> 00:08:41,140
I can't help but admire myself.

134
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:43,260
So, you enjoy playing

135
00:08:44,730 --> 00:08:47,140
these games during the interrogation.

136
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:48,610
Start talking.

137
00:08:49,180 --> 00:08:50,570
The military fund
mysteriously disappeared.

138
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:52,660
What's really going on here?

139
00:08:53,210 --> 00:08:54,260
Who's the one that made you

140
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:55,570
commit this felon?

141
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:58,140
The person behind it all

142
00:08:59,210 --> 00:09:01,020
is right there tonight.

143
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:03,780
You mean Mr. Yuan?

144
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:05,210
It's Du Liang, obviously.

145
00:09:05,730 --> 00:09:07,380
The military fund was in his mansion,

146
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,660
and so was I.

147
00:09:10,730 --> 00:09:12,450
If I stole them,

148
00:09:13,180 --> 00:09:14,940
it was under his orders.

149
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:16,690
He

150
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:18,970
is the true mastermind.

151
00:09:22,810 --> 00:09:24,570
Blaming everything on a dead man,

152
00:09:24,690 --> 00:09:25,730
do you really think I'd believe that?

153
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:27,690
A mere fifth-rank director

154
00:09:28,450 --> 00:09:29,900
daring to embezzle
all the military fund

155
00:09:30,450 --> 00:09:31,940
and stash it in his own home?

156
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:33,810
Even if he had the nerve,

157
00:09:34,660 --> 00:09:35,490
someone

158
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:36,690
must have emboldened him,

159
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:39,900
don't you think?

160
00:09:41,260 --> 00:09:43,060
This is exactly
what you wanted, isn't it?

161
00:09:43,730 --> 00:09:44,490
Honestly,

162
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,780
you didn't even need to torture me.

163
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:47,330
I would have confessed
everything anyway.

164
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:50,780
Just tell me who you want me to accuse:

165
00:09:51,140 --> 00:09:51,780
a general,

166
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:52,900
a minister,

167
00:09:53,210 --> 00:09:54,060
or the Grand Chancellor.

168
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:56,300
Be it a minor offense

169
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:58,690
or a crime that wipes out
an entire lineage,

170
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:02,090
I'll sign wherever you want.

171
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:06,810
Listen,

172
00:10:07,450 --> 00:10:08,330
it's only the Hour of Hai.

173
00:10:10,330 --> 00:10:11,450
Seeing you like this

174
00:10:12,490 --> 00:10:13,380
is quite disappointing.

175
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,330
I had an entire night

176
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,210
prepared just for you,

177
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:19,260
with tortures no one

178
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:21,060
has ever had the privilege
of experiencing.

179
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:22,660
The Golden Cauldron,

180
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:24,330
the Sea of Serpents,

181
00:10:24,970 --> 00:10:25,810
the Bone Flute…

182
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:27,260
Without a little persuasion,

183
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:29,660
the truth never comes out.

184
00:10:30,780 --> 00:10:31,900
Now, I understand.

185
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:35,850
Of all the people you've interrogated,

186
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,540
which ones

187
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,490
bring you the greatest thrill?

188
00:10:42,830 --> 00:10:43,740
I'd guess

189
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:47,830
it's the powerful and noble.

190
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:49,350
Seeing them

191
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:52,260
dragged from their high status
into the filth,

192
00:10:52,620 --> 00:10:55,350
with their pride
shattered piece by piece.

193
00:10:56,020 --> 00:10:57,230
That irony

194
00:10:58,190 --> 00:11:00,230
is what excites you the most,

195
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:02,070
isn't it?

196
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:13,070
Master.

197
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:13,830
Mr. Zhang.

198
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:16,590
Go ahead.

199
00:11:16,990 --> 00:11:17,990
Tell us the situation tonight.

200
00:11:18,430 --> 00:11:18,860
Yes, sir.

201
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:20,950
Mr. Yuan brought people

202
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:21,950
into Du Liang's mansion tonight

203
00:11:22,350 --> 00:11:23,470
and found the missing military fund.

204
00:11:24,070 --> 00:11:25,070
Du Liang has been executed

205
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:25,950
for embezzling the fund.

206
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:38,500
He... he accidentally died from a fall.

207
00:11:43,310 --> 00:11:44,020
Mr. Zhang,

208
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:47,860
I think Cheng Hui
is somewhat undervalued.

209
00:11:48,070 --> 00:11:48,990
The Ministry of Justice

210
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:50,380
still has positions to fill, doesn't it?

211
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:54,380
Thank you, Master.

212
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:56,310
I will never forget this favor.

213
00:11:57,430 --> 00:11:59,470
I'll also ensure your sister

214
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,620
and mother

215
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:02,310
are well taken care of.

216
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:03,380
Thank you, Master.

217
00:12:03,590 --> 00:12:04,110
You may rise.

218
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:04,900
Yes, sir.

219
00:12:07,350 --> 00:12:08,380
Also, Ye Ping'an

220
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,740
has been arrested by Li Jun

221
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:10,990
and is being interrogated
overnight in the prison.

222
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:24,070
This matter

223
00:12:25,070 --> 00:12:26,540
must be settled tonight.

224
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:31,140
Understood.

225
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:37,350
For such a major case,

226
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:38,310
the Ministry of Justice

227
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:39,620
needs to draft a memorandum.

228
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:40,620
To report to the palace,

229
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,070
it will have to wait until tomorrow.

230
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:45,070
Mr. Hai,

231
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:46,230
I must take my leave now.

232
00:12:46,950 --> 00:12:47,540
I won't see you off.

233
00:12:52,430 --> 00:12:53,230
Send someone to keep an eye on Cheng Hui

234
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:54,740
and see

235
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:56,950
if he can eliminate Ye Ping'an.

236
00:12:57,430 --> 00:12:57,950
Yes, sir.

237
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:04,020
Why do you suspect

238
00:13:04,230 --> 00:13:04,990
[Hidden chamber]
Ye Ping'an is the survivor

239
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:07,620
of the censor's case?

240
00:13:09,190 --> 00:13:10,830
When the Zheng Yuan case happened,

241
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:11,620
I thought

242
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:12,830
she was just a scapegoat.

243
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:14,350
But to my surprise,

244
00:13:14,780 --> 00:13:15,590
she used the case

245
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:16,830
to secure an official position.

246
00:13:17,310 --> 00:13:17,740
Moreover,

247
00:13:17,950 --> 00:13:19,900
she was fully aware
of Du Liang's embezzlement

248
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:21,350
and sought to use
the military fund case

249
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:22,430
to bring him down when she came to me.

250
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:24,830
That's when I realized
that she was a meticulous person

251
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:27,020
and certainly not someone
to be underestimated.

252
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:28,830
At my mother's birthday banquet,

253
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,310
the person involved in the censor's case

254
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,260
came to offer his congratulations.

255
00:13:31,710 --> 00:13:33,110
The Seven-Petal Epiphyllum mark

256
00:13:33,230 --> 00:13:34,660
on his concubine's arm

257
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:37,430
caught Yan's attention,
and she stared at it for a long while.

258
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:38,830
I guided her

259
00:13:38,830 --> 00:13:39,900
to draw it,

260
00:13:40,590 --> 00:13:41,590
and it turned out

261
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:43,350
that she was indeed a victim

262
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:44,380
in the censor's case.

263
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:46,020
With a meticulous mind

264
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:47,950
and the audacity
to involve herself in this,

265
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,990
she's someone who seeks
to dominate others' wills.

266
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:52,260
Such a person

267
00:13:52,780 --> 00:13:53,780
must be eradicated.

268
00:13:56,380 --> 00:13:58,070
Who knew you'd be the one
who truly understands me?

269
00:13:59,070 --> 00:14:00,900
Using torture devices
to strip away their identities.

270
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:03,230
Now that's the ultimate art.

271
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:04,660
But alas.

272
00:14:06,190 --> 00:14:06,860
Tell me

273
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:09,020
who exactly instructed

274
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:10,860
Du Liang to rob the military fund

275
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:12,500
from the official road.

276
00:14:14,230 --> 00:14:16,260
Of course, it's someone
from a noble family.

277
00:14:19,230 --> 00:14:20,310
Speaking of nobility,

278
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:22,900
you came from humble origins,

279
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:25,070
struggling for years
before becoming an official.

280
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:26,660
But the aristocracy,

281
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:28,140
disdainful of your background,

282
00:14:28,350 --> 00:14:30,020
hindered your promotion.

283
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:31,710
From that point onward,

284
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:33,310
you harbored hatred for them,

285
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:36,380
even though the Right Chancellor,
Fu Shengjun,

286
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:37,860
considered you a close friend.

287
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,990
Yet, you still dragged him

288
00:14:40,540 --> 00:14:42,780
into a place of no return.

289
00:14:45,020 --> 00:14:45,950
A close friend?

290
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:50,140
Fu Shengjun was always high and mighty,

291
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:51,860
and deep down, he saw me

292
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:52,660
as nothing more than a plaything.

293
00:14:53,430 --> 00:14:54,140
All of you

294
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,540
treat me like a mad dog,

295
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:57,740
but this mad dog

296
00:14:58,430 --> 00:14:59,990
has helped Her Majesty
clear countless obstacles.

297
00:14:59,990 --> 00:15:01,020
Am I wrong for doing that?

298
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,070
Then why did you kill

299
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:05,260
that sick commoner?

300
00:15:06,350 --> 00:15:07,350
How many of the common folk's blood

301
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:09,660
is on your hands?

302
00:15:12,110 --> 00:15:13,110
Are you trying to say

303
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,140
that we both come
from humble beginnings,

304
00:15:17,660 --> 00:15:19,190
born of the same background,

305
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:22,350
so there's no need
to turn against each other?

306
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:25,900
Too bad,

307
00:15:26,110 --> 00:15:27,430
your silver tongue

308
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:29,070
doesn't work on me.

309
00:15:31,780 --> 00:15:33,020
During every interrogation,

310
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:36,380
the most boring part for you

311
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:39,380
is when the person dies,

312
00:15:40,070 --> 00:15:41,860
no longer struggling or moving.

313
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:43,430
So,

314
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:46,780
for a frail prisoner like me,

315
00:15:48,020 --> 00:15:50,020
I have a unique method of torture,

316
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:52,900
one that's effective
but won't cause serious harm.

317
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:54,860
Interested?

318
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:57,540
I'm listening.

319
00:15:58,860 --> 00:16:01,740
Dragon scales blanket the bed,
the waves dampening the air.

320
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:05,830
Blood droplets fall as the lady weeps.

321
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:09,140
Take the fish scales as dragon scales,

322
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:10,830
embedding them into the skin

323
00:16:11,310 --> 00:16:13,140
before removing them later.

324
00:16:13,900 --> 00:16:15,380
The blood will then stain the bamboo.

325
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,430
This

326
00:16:18,230 --> 00:16:20,190
is the weeping of the lady.

327
00:16:23,070 --> 00:16:23,710
Someone,

328
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:26,830
go get me some fish right now!

329
00:16:27,260 --> 00:16:28,260
It's already curfew.

330
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:29,260
Where can I possibly get any fish?

331
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,310
Just do whatever you can to get them!

332
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:31,990
All right.

333
00:16:32,260 --> 00:16:32,950
Take her back to the cell

334
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:34,620
and let her rest.

335
00:16:35,310 --> 00:16:37,430
We'll deal with her properly later.

336
00:16:37,430 --> 00:16:39,820
[Ministry of Justice]

337
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,310
It's already so late.

338
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:44,660
Where are we supposed to find fish?

339
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:45,900
He's already torturing the prisoner,

340
00:16:45,950 --> 00:16:46,830
now he's taking it out on us too.

341
00:16:47,350 --> 00:16:47,990
I know, right?

342
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:52,620
Fish?

