00:17:05,430 --> 00:17:06,670
The message Ping'an can convey

347
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:07,260
is quite limited,

348
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:08,950
so it must point

349
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:10,870
to a very specific location.

350
00:17:13,390 --> 00:17:14,230
So it's...

351
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,230
- The black market.
- The black market.

352
00:17:16,390 --> 00:17:16,910
That's right.

353
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:18,340
The only place
where we can buy fish after curfew

354
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:19,870
is the black market.

355
00:17:21,630 --> 00:17:22,630
I understand what Ping'an means now.

356
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:24,100
We need to head there quickly.

357
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:47,820
Just

358
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:49,020
drink this.

359
00:17:52,670 --> 00:17:53,430
If you kill me,

360
00:17:53,910 --> 00:17:54,910
not only will you not earn any merit,

361
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:55,990
but you'll also end up dead.

362
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:57,430
What nonsense are you talking about?

363
00:17:58,230 --> 00:17:58,780
Drink this!

364
00:17:59,230 --> 00:18:00,300
Before Du Liang died,

365
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:01,820
he told me a secret.

366
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:03,340
You saw it too, didn't you?

367
00:18:03,910 --> 00:18:05,990
It's very important
for those behind you.

368
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:14,340
What did he tell you?

369
00:18:15,430 --> 00:18:17,020
Du Liang bribed many people,

370
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:19,260
and he kept a record

371
00:18:19,710 --> 00:18:20,710
of all his transactions.

372
00:18:21,190 --> 00:18:22,230
If things go south,

373
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:25,630
this ledger will be made public,

374
00:18:25,950 --> 00:18:26,990
and your backers

375
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:28,780
will be in serious trouble.

376
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:30,470
However, if you

377
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:32,260
manage to get it,

378
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:34,260
you'll be making a great contribution.

379
00:18:37,390 --> 00:18:38,150
So where is it?

380
00:18:38,630 --> 00:18:39,150
Tell me!

381
00:18:39,990 --> 00:18:40,990
The fish store in the black market.

382
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:58,710
Shaocheng,

383
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:00,230
what are you doing?

384
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:02,260
My old man was a blacksmith.

385
00:19:03,990 --> 00:19:05,150
He could turn any scrap metal

386
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:07,390
into something useful

387
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:08,710
with his hammer.

388
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,870
What are you trying to make?

389
00:19:15,870 --> 00:19:16,870
Badges for my family.

390
00:19:22,470 --> 00:19:23,950
You're bottling up too much inside.

391
00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:25,540
It's going to crush you.

392
00:19:25,910 --> 00:19:26,950
You can't just take it out

393
00:19:27,150 --> 00:19:28,910
on the metal

394
00:19:29,390 --> 00:19:31,150
and expect it to go away.

395
00:19:36,470 --> 00:19:37,020
Mr. Gu,

396
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:39,500
you know,

397
00:19:41,340 --> 00:19:42,150
sometimes,

398
00:19:44,060 --> 00:19:46,260
I feel that my hands are tainted.

399
00:19:47,230 --> 00:19:48,100
So, I keep trying

400
00:19:48,150 --> 00:19:49,150
to wash them with liquor,

401
00:19:50,300 --> 00:19:51,340
but no matter how much I try,

402
00:19:51,340 --> 00:19:52,630
I can't get rid of the smell of blood.

403
00:19:53,990 --> 00:19:54,910
After that, my heart

404
00:19:56,630 --> 00:19:57,820
just becomes harder

405
00:19:59,430 --> 00:20:00,100
and colder.

406
00:20:02,390 --> 00:20:03,060
Actually,

407
00:20:04,990 --> 00:20:07,500
if you take matters into your own hands
in the military fund case,

408
00:20:07,710 --> 00:20:08,630
then Ye Ping'an...

409
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:10,020
Right now, the most important thing

410
00:20:10,060 --> 00:20:11,390
is to gain the trust
of the Mei alliance.

411
00:20:13,100 --> 00:20:13,870
Everyone

412
00:20:13,910 --> 00:20:14,710
has their own path to follow.

413
00:20:15,430 --> 00:20:16,430
Once you've made your choice,

414
00:20:17,910 --> 00:20:19,100
you shouldn't pin your hopes

415
00:20:19,100 --> 00:20:20,430
on others.

416
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:23,580
I think this way,

417
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:26,780
and so does Ye Ping'an.

418
00:20:28,820 --> 00:20:29,500
If she

419
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:30,910
can't even save herself,

420
00:20:32,630 --> 00:20:34,470
with so many dangers ahead,

421
00:20:36,910 --> 00:20:38,230
she'll die sooner or later.

422
00:20:40,150 --> 00:20:41,630
So, why should I
go out of my way for her?

423
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:48,540
Someone wants to kill you?

424
00:20:49,430 --> 00:20:50,060
Why?

425
00:20:51,430 --> 00:20:52,870
Before Du Liang died,

426
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:55,580
he told me about a list of bribes

427
00:20:56,060 --> 00:20:57,150
hidden in the black market.

428
00:20:58,950 --> 00:21:01,500
Instead of making things difficult

429
00:21:01,630 --> 00:21:03,060
for someone insignificant like me,

430
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,300
you would be better off

431
00:21:05,710 --> 00:21:07,150
following those trying to kill me

432
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,230
and uncovering

433
00:21:10,340 --> 00:21:11,910
the powerful officials behind it.

434
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:13,670
That way,

435
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:17,540
you'll earn a far greater reward.

436
00:21:21,670 --> 00:21:22,710
Stay here and keep your eyes on her.

437
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:23,470
Don't go anywhere.

438
00:21:23,710 --> 00:21:24,190
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

439
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:36,230
Come here

440
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:37,260
and take a look.

441
00:21:37,670 --> 00:21:38,630
These are all rare treasures.

442
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:39,990
Feel free to have a look.

443
00:21:40,950 --> 00:21:41,950
Hey, do you want to take a look?

444
00:21:43,020 --> 00:21:43,580
Don't leave just yet.

445
00:21:44,430 --> 00:21:45,150
Have a browse.

446
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:46,230
Everything here is top-notch.

447
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:54,060
Buy it if you want,

448
00:21:54,390 --> 00:21:54,950
or just leave.

449
00:22:01,470 --> 00:22:01,950
Nice liquor!

450
00:22:20,580 --> 00:22:21,190
Sir.

451
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:22,910
Are you here to buy fish?

452
00:22:23,260 --> 00:22:23,820
They're freshly killed.

453
00:22:25,710 --> 00:22:26,580
I work for Mr. Du.

454
00:22:27,150 --> 00:22:27,710
I'm here to retrieve

455
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:28,990
the ledger he entrusted to you.

456
00:22:29,780 --> 00:22:30,430
Ledger?

457
00:22:30,950 --> 00:22:31,740
What ledger?

458
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:32,820
We just sell fish here.

459
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:33,910
We don't have anything like that.

460
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:41,950
Sir, wait.

461
00:22:42,340 --> 00:22:43,190
I remember now.

462
00:22:43,710 --> 00:22:45,150
There was

463
00:22:45,470 --> 00:22:46,020
a Mr. Du

464
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:47,820
who left something here.

465
00:22:48,670 --> 00:22:49,390
What was it called?

466
00:22:49,580 --> 00:22:50,190
A copper scroll?

467
00:22:51,260 --> 00:22:52,470
Is that what you're referring to?

468
00:22:52,630 --> 00:22:52,870
Yes,

469
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:54,260
the copper scroll is the ledger.

470
00:22:54,390 --> 00:22:54,780
Give it to me.

471
00:22:54,950 --> 00:22:56,340
You'll need the owner's token

472
00:22:56,390 --> 00:22:57,060
to get it.

473
00:22:57,190 --> 00:22:57,910
Do you have it?

474
00:22:58,990 --> 00:22:59,630
I... I do.

475
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,260
One moment, please.

476
00:23:00,580 --> 00:23:01,300
Why didn't you say so earlier?

477
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:04,670
Hand over the copper scroll.

478
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:05,470
All right.

479
00:23:05,670 --> 00:23:06,300
Please stay calm.

480
00:23:06,390 --> 00:23:06,990
Give it to me now!

481
00:23:06,990 --> 00:23:07,910
All right.

482
00:23:30,540 --> 00:23:31,100
Mr. Li!

483
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:33,910
Go after him!

484
00:23:40,630 --> 00:23:41,500
Why are there two groups of people here?

485
00:23:43,390 --> 00:23:44,100
We make a good team.

486
00:23:45,390 --> 00:23:46,670
Ping'an must have tricked them

487
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:48,820
into coming for Du Liang's ledger

488
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,780
to buy some time.

489
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,580
I gave him an empty copper scroll.

490
00:23:53,100 --> 00:23:54,100
It's a good thing you reacted quickly.

491
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:54,820
But

492
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:55,470
the copper scroll

493
00:23:55,470 --> 00:23:56,150
will likely be exposed soon enough.

494
00:23:56,670 --> 00:23:57,820
Every moment we delay
is a moment gained.

495
00:23:58,580 --> 00:23:59,950
The reason Li Jun is here

496
00:24:00,580 --> 00:24:01,470
is that Ping'an

497
00:24:01,580 --> 00:24:02,740
wants him

498
00:24:03,260 --> 00:24:04,540
