499
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:12,060
Master,

500
00:24:12,740 --> 00:24:13,910
the one monitoring
Cheng Hui has informed us

501
00:24:14,150 --> 00:24:14,870
that he suddenly left the prison

502
00:24:14,870 --> 00:24:15,990
and headed for the black market

503
00:24:16,020 --> 00:24:16,540
for some unknown reasons.

504
00:24:20,150 --> 00:24:20,950
That means

505
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:23,470
he didn't manage

506
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:25,390
to kill Ye Ping'an.

507
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:26,870
What should we do now?

508
00:24:39,820 --> 00:24:40,230
Split up and pursue.

509
00:24:40,670 --> 00:24:41,710
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

510
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:44,190
Cheng Hui.

511
00:24:50,900 --> 00:24:51,540
I got it.

512
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:53,100
[The steward of Hai Mansion]

513
00:24:53,950 --> 00:24:56,190
Mr. Hai
will take good care of your family.

514
00:24:56,710 --> 00:24:57,340
Don't worry.

515
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:00,670
Over there!

516
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:06,500
Tell me.

517
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:07,820
Who was it that tried to kill you?

518
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:09,630
My mother

519
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:11,430
can finally live a good life.

520
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:22,630
Mr. Li,

521
00:25:22,710 --> 00:25:23,340
it's empty.

522
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:24,870
In such a short time,

523
00:25:25,020 --> 00:25:26,300
they couldn't have taken the ledger.

524
00:25:26,870 --> 00:25:27,820
Could we have been tricked?

525
00:25:28,780 --> 00:25:29,950
How dare you trick me!

526
00:25:32,630 --> 00:25:33,300
Ye Ping'an!

527
00:25:34,150 --> 00:25:35,340
I'm going to skin you alive!

528
00:25:43,390 --> 00:25:44,020
Mr. Li.

529
00:25:50,300 --> 00:25:50,870
You...

530
00:25:52,230 --> 00:25:53,430
You didn't manage to catch anyone?

531
00:25:53,910 --> 00:25:54,710
Catch my foot.

532
00:25:55,470 --> 00:25:56,300
That person named Cheng Hui

533
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,020
has already been silenced.

534
00:25:57,780 --> 00:25:58,630
The Du Liang ledger you mentioned

535
00:25:58,630 --> 00:26:00,100
is nothing but a fabrication.

536
00:26:01,020 --> 00:26:02,150
You wanted to use me

537
00:26:02,150 --> 00:26:03,260
to help catch the people behind this.

538
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:04,950
You're still under suspicion,

539
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:06,340
yet you dared to deceive me.

540
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:07,780
I'll let you experience

541
00:26:08,150 --> 00:26:09,430
all the torture devices in this prison.

542
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:15,190
Miss Wu is here.

543
00:26:25,150 --> 00:26:25,910
Here's Her Majesty's verbal decree.

544
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:26,910
Li Jun.

545
00:26:27,390 --> 00:26:28,910
Ye Ping'an is the commissioner
I appointed.

546
00:26:29,150 --> 00:26:30,150
How dare you arrest her without cause.

547
00:26:30,710 --> 00:26:31,470
I command you

548
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:33,470
