and drop the charges.

549
00:26:34,060 --> 00:26:35,260
I have failed to understand
Her Majesty's intentions.

550
00:26:35,740 --> 00:26:36,300
I am guilty.

551
00:26:36,710 --> 00:26:37,470
- I...
- Mr. Li,

552
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:38,780
if you continue to act so recklessly,

553
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,300
those tortures of yours

554
00:26:40,950 --> 00:26:41,710
might just

555
00:26:42,230 --> 00:26:43,950
be used on you.

556
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:45,780
Now, get out of here!

557
00:26:48,300 --> 00:26:48,870
Let's go.

558
00:27:08,060 --> 00:27:09,540
You're in such a hurry to see me.

559
00:27:10,150 --> 00:27:11,300
Has there been any progress

560
00:27:11,780 --> 00:27:12,780
