00:27:18,150 --> 00:27:19,580
However, once I finish this case,

565
00:27:20,470 --> 00:27:21,820
I fear I will no longer have the chance

566
00:27:23,230 --> 00:27:24,470
to return this token

567
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:26,780
to Your Majesty personally.

568
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:29,820
What do you mean by that?

569
00:27:30,670 --> 00:27:31,540
I have said before

570
00:27:32,470 --> 00:27:33,260
that I am willing
to be the harsh remedy

571
00:27:33,870 --> 00:27:35,340
